          "reviewBody": "Today I was going to pick up my daughter from school two boys from lycee sat beside me. They started their conversation with two to three slangs in every sentence. It was not at all expected. Even the auto driver was feeling irritated. They were openly discussing about taking drugs during Puja and passing lure remarks regarding women. I had no idea about this school but it is however not expected. I hope after seeing this message the teachers will take care about their students.",
