          "reviewBody": "Lots of memories to cherish here and teachers who really cares of their students, with ample notes, any issues or special classes, special activity sessions and lots of fun and enjoyment. Even when I walk across Hindustan park it's a nostalgia to see the LYCEE logo, feel proud of. #1998 ICSE",
