            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Worst school I have seen in my life. The  teachers  does not know actually how to talk decently with the parents and students also . Yeah  I was not so good in studies but they don't  have any  right to say any one abnormal by the way let me say this that abnormal is commencing with BBA and got a good job also . I am glad to be a student of Calcutta Public School from where I have passed  my  ISC examination . At least they tried to understand my problems and tried to help me out . Actually teachers of Lycee should learn how to behave before they teach  students how to behave.\nAfter  I passed out from I always discouraged others who wanted to take admission in this school.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
