          "reviewBody": "I studied here for 3 years(batch of 2013) and those were the best 3 years of my school life. The best things about lycee are its environment and the teachers. They are very helpful, non judgemental and friendly. The english faculty was amazing.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
